These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, dancing, reading
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, spy, superhero
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, folk, trance
There 3 different types of food: plum, eggplant, radish
1. the person eating plum is on the right of the fan of trance##1
2. the fan of blues is on the left of the person eating radish##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching superhero movies##2
4. the person eating plum is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the fan of trance is the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Hobby         | dancing | baking   | reading   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | disaster | superhero |
| Music-Genre   | trance  | blues    | folk      |
| Food     | eggplant     | plum      | radish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
There 3 different types of food: kale, raspberry, tomato
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, fanta
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, japanese, pakistani
3 different pets are kept: frog, goat, guinea-pig
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the pakistani is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person eating raspberry is the pakistani##1
4. the person eating kale is the japanese##1
5. the owner of the frog is between the person drinking lemonade and the person eating tomato##2
6. the person eating tomato is the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Food          | raspberry  | kale     | tomato     |
| Beverage   | lemonade     | fanta     | juice      |
| Nationality   | pakistani  | japanese | australian |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | frog     | goat       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, kale, orange
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, doctor, paramedic
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, rock, blues
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, snake
1. the bartender is on the left of the fan of blues##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is between the paramedic and the fan of blues##2
3. the person eating eggplant is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is the person eating kale##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Food          | eggplant  | orange     | kale     |
| Job           | paramedic | bartender  | doctor   |
| Music-Genre   | electronic  | rock    | blues |
| Pet           | snake     | chinchilla | goldfish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, malaysian, indonesian
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, paramedic, scientist
3 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, guinea-pig
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, rugby, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the malaysian is on the right of the scientist##1
3. the indonesian is between the paramedic and the owner of the cat##2
4. the malaysian is the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Nationality    | egyptian       | indonesian  | malaysian   |
| Job     | paramedic    | scientist  | journalist |
| Pet     | chinchilla   | guinea-pig | cat        |
| Sport   | snowboarding | rowing     | rugby      |

