.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-5::.
There 3 different types of food: carrot, cherry, plum
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, filmmaking, photography
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, funk, gospel
House: cottage, cape-cod, palace
1. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of funk##1
2. the cottage house is between the fan of gospel and the person who's hobby is photography##2
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is the cape-cod house##1
4. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating plum##1
5. the cottage house is on the left of the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Food          | plum    | carrot     | cherry      |
| Hobby         | cooking | filmmaking | photography |
| Music-Genre   | gospel  | funk       | disco       |
| House           | cape-cod     | cottage       | palace     |

