.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-8::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, soy-milk, water
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, cooking, brazilian-climbing
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, dressmaker, journalist
There are 3 different nationalities: french, american, brazilian
1. the journalist is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the american##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
4. the architect is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person drinking water##2
5. the person drinking soy-milk is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Beverage      | cola       | soy-milk      | water      |
| Hobby         | cooking    | brazilian-climbing | chess      |
| Job           | journalist | architect     | dressmaker |
| Nationality   | american     | brazilian          | french       |

