.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-12::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, tea
The people have 3 different jobs:  firefighter, security-guard, social-worker
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: horror, musical, sports
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, rock-climbing, singing
1. the person drinking iced-tea is the social-worker##1
2. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is between the security-guard and the person watching musical movies##2
6. the person watching horror movies is the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |       3        |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | iced-tea      | tea            |
| Job           | firefighter | social-worker | security-guard |
| Movie-Genre   | musical     | sports        | horror         |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing  | chess    | singing        |

