The people use 3 different means of transport: train, jet-ski, snowmobile
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, pony, snake
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, lacrosse, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the pilot is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
3. the nurse is between the person driving the snowmobile and the owner of the snake##2
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |      3      |
| Job           | architect | nurse        | pilot       |
| Transport   | train | jet-ski | snowmobile |
| Pet           | snake     | pony         | guinea-pig  |
| Sport         | lacrosse  | tennis       | basketball  |

