.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-15::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, cherry, potato
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, punk, trance
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, nigerian, spanish
City: rome, san-francisco, liverpool
1. the fan of trance is on the left of the nigerian##1
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is between the fan of trance and the spanish##2
3. the person traveling to rome is on the far right##1
4. the person eating cherry is between the fan of trance and the person eating artichoke##2
5. the fan of punk is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Food          | potato  | cherry   | artichoke |
| Music-Genre   | trance  | punk     | classical |
| Nationality   | chinese | nigerian | spanish   |
| City     | liverpool   | san-francisco   | rome      |

