.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-16::.
House: victorian, craftsman, palace
3 different pets are kept: horse, mouse, rat
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, golf, parkour
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, train, tram
1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person driving the train##1
2. the owner of the rat is between the person driving the boat and the owner of the horse##2
3. the palace house is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is golf is the person driving the boat##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the victorian house##1
6. the victorian house is on the left of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |      3       |
| House       | palace | victorian | craftsman |
| Pet         | horse   | rat       | mouse        |
| Sport       | parkour | cricket   | golf         |
| Transport   | tram    | train     | boat         |

