There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, german, turkish
3 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, pony
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, rock-climbing, chess
1. the german is between the person who's hobby is chess and the egyptian##2
2. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the fan of electronic is the owner of the dog##1
4. the owner of the pony is the fan of disco##1
5. the person who's hobby is reading is the owner of the hamster##1
6. the egyptian is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | disco  | folk     |
| Nationality   | turkish    | german | egyptian |
| Pet           | dog        | pony   | hamster  |
| Hobby     | chess      | rock-climbing   | reading |

